<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10854</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个狱警在美罗城监狱里巡逻。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“关灯！”她大声喊道，“睡觉时间到了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>牢房里，普雷斯托嘟囔着爬上了床。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>威格尔斯夫人和怪人博士在旁边的牢房里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我讨厌睡觉时间！”威格尔斯夫人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42351</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狱警没有理坏人们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42351</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45351</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她走到一个拐角。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45351</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，她大吃一惊。墙上有一个巨大的洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56104</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狱警大声喊道：“犯人逃走了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56104</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“特勒尔去哪里了？”杰克问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西和玛拉在杰克家外面等他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74854</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他今天会迟到一会儿。”罗西说，“ 我们先走吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74854</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78857</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>三个朋友沿着人行道走着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78857</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83105</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“特勒尔为什么会迟到呢？”杰克问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83105</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉咯咯笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90545</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他可能在家想办法找出火箭女孩儿到底是谁呢！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90545</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西也笑了。“不是，他约了牙医。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98246</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们很快到了学校。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他们快到教室的时候，罗西听到她的手表在响。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很快就进去。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得……嗯……去洗手间。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117446</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西躲进一个拐角。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117446</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122039</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“布洛姆市长！”她小声说，“一切都好吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122039</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124960</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>市长看起来很困惑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124960</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127573</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不是很好，火箭女孩儿！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127573</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我觉得有人从美罗城监狱逃走了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135570</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁？”罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135570</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138705</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道。”布洛姆市长说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138705</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“狱警们查了一整夜牢房。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有的犯人都在。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西挠了挠头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151135</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不明白，市长。那您为什么说有人逃走了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155638</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“监狱墙上有一个大洞。”布洛姆市长说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155638</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157886</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很让人怀疑。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157886</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好的，市长！”罗西说，“我马上赶到！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168387</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，学校的门猛地被打开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>轰！空中传来很大的嗡嗡声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西合上了手表。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175637</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179387</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她感到有一股无形的力量在拉她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183231</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老师们和学生们呼啦一下飞走了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183231</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186069</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>好像被吸尘器吸走了一样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190069</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西用她超级力量在地上站稳了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192819</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉和杰克飞走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192819</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196819</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”玛拉尖叫着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196819</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200819</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“救命啊！”杰克大声喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200819</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205070</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>书、铅笔、纸从书包里掉了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205070</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>走廊里一片混乱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211821</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，所有人都不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211821</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呀！”罗西想，“怎么回事啊？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216320</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221069</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯？”特勒尔说，“发生了什么事？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224067</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他站在美罗城小学前面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224067</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228570</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>路上到处都是纸和书。门大开着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228570</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232321</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔跑进了学校。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看到罗西跑进了走廊尽头的洗手间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔沿着走廊跑过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿，洗手间的门哐地打开，火箭女孩儿跑了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>